            <div class="col-md-6 px-0">
              <h1 class="display-4 fst-italic">About OzarkEats</h1>
              <p class="lead my-3">
                <span class="fst-italic">OzarkEats</span> is a simple
                application that allows users to create, edit, and delete
                restaurants that are located right here in the
                <span class="fst-italic">Ozarks</span>. It is a work in progress
                but we are excited to see what you create!
              </p>
