                <h2 class="blog-post-title pb-4 mb-4 fst-italic">
                  Getting started tips from the developer
                </h2>
                <p class="blog-post-meta border-bottom">
                  <span class="fst-italic">
                    November 19, 2021 | Rogersville, Missouri
                  </span>
                  <br />
                  By:
                  <a href="#"><%= user.firstName %> <%= user.lastName %> </a>
                </p>
                <h3 class="blog-post-title" id="posts">Getting started and making posts</h3>
                <p>
                  To get started, you will need to create a <span class="fst-italic"><a href="/register">New User</a></span> account.
                    Once you have created an account, you will be able to <span class="fst-italic"><a href="/login">Log In</a></span>
                    and create, edit, and delete restaurants. You will also be
                    able to view all of the restaurants that are currently
                    available. You will also be able to view the reviews that
                    have been written for each restaurant.

                </p>
                <hr />
                <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                  How to create a restaurant
                </h3>
                <p>
                  To create a restaurant, you will need to log in.
                  Once you are logged in, you will be able to click on the
                  <span class="fst-italic"><a href="/restaurants/new">Create Restaurant</a></span> button
                  and fill out the form. Once you have filled out the form,
                  you will be able to click on the <span class="fst-italic">Submit</span>
                  button. Once you have submitted the form, you will be
                  redirected to the Restaurant's Show Page
                  page.
                </p>
                <hr />
                <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                  How to edit a restaurant
                </h3>
                <p>
                  To edit a restaurant restaurant you created, you will need to be logged in.
                  Once you are logged in, you will be able to click on the <span class="fst-italic">Update</span> button under your listing
                  and fill out the form. Once you have filled out the form,
                  you will be able to click on the <span class="fst-italic">Update</span>
                  button. Once you have submitted the form, you will be
                  redirected to the <span class="fst-italic">Restaurant's Show</span>
                  page.
                </p>
                <hr />
                <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                  How to delete a restaurant
                </h3>
                <p>
                  To delete a restaurant you created, just click on the
                  <span class="fst-italic">Delete</span> button located on the restaurant show page.
                You will be
                  redirected to the <span class="fst-italic"><a href="/restaurants">Restaurants</a></span>
                  page.
                </p>
                <hr />
                <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                  How to view all restaurants
                </h3>
                <p>
                  To view all restaurants, just click on the
                  <span class="fst-italic"><a href="/restaurants">Restaurants</a></span> button
                  and you will be
                  redirected to the <span class="fst-italic">Restaurants</span>
                  page.
                </p>
                <hr />
                <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                  How to view a restaurant
                </h3>
                <p>
                  To view a restaurant, just click on the
                  <a href="">View</a></span> button
                  and you will be
                  redirected to the <span class="fst-italic">Restaurant</span>
                  page.
                </p>
                <hr />
                <h3 class="blog-post-title" id="reviews">
                  How to create a review
                </h3>
                <p>
                  To create a review, you will need to be logged in.
                  Once you are logged in, you will be able to click on the
                  star rating and fill out the review field. 1 star is terrible, 5 stars is great.
                    Once you have filled out the form, you will be able to click on the <span class="fst-italic">Submit</span>
                </p>
                <hr />
                <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                  How to delete a review
                </h3>
                <p>
                  To delete a review, you will need to be logged in.
                  Once you are logged in, you will be able to click on the
                  <a href="">Delete</a></span> button
                  and you will be
                  redirected to the <span class="fst-italic">Restaurant</span>
                  page.
                </p>
                <hr />
                <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                  Random restaurant feature
                </h3>
                <p>
                This feature was added for those looking for quick and easy ways to find a restaurant when indecisive.
                  To view a random restaurant, just click on the
                  <a href="">Random</a></span> button
                  and you will be
                  redirected to a random <span class="fst-italic">Restaurant</span>
                  page.
                </p>
                </article>
                <hr>
