                <article class="blog-post">
                    <h2 class="blog-post-title pb-4 mb-4 fst-italic">
                      Contact, Search, Password Reset and Email Verification
                    </h2>
                    <p class="blog-post-meta border-bottom">
                      <span class="fst-italic">
                        November 19, 2021 | Rogersville, Missouri
                      </span>
                      <br />
                      By:
                      <a href="#"><%= user.firstName %> <%= user.lastName %> </a>
                    </p>
                    <h3 class="blog-post-title" id="contact">Contact form</h3>
                    <p>
                        To reach out and send us a message we created a contact form.
                        You can reach out to us by filling out the form and clicking on the <span class="fst-italic">Submit</span>
                        button. We'll get back to you as soon as possible.

                    </p>
                    <hr />
                    <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                      Added a search feature
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        To search for a restaurant, you can either use the home page or the navigation menu to search for a restaurant.
                        You can search for a restaurant by entering the name or the description of the restaurant in the search bar.

                    </p>
                    <hr />
                    <h3 class="blog-post-title" id="password">
                      Added password reset
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        To reset your password, you can click on the <span class="fst-italic">Reset link</span> on the login page.
                        You will be redirected to the <span class="fst-italic">Forgot Password</span> page.
                        Once you have filled out the form, you will be able to click on the <span class="fst-italic">Submit</span>
                        button. Once you have submitted the form, you will be
                        redirected to the <span class="fst-italic">Reset Password</span>
                        page.
                    </p>
                    <hr />
                    <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                      Added email confirmation
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        To confirm your email, you can click "Verify Email" or paste the verification url in your search bar if your email doesn't support html.
                        You will be redirected to the <span class="fst-italic">Confirm Email</span> page.
                        Once you have clicked on the <span class="fst-italic">Verify Email</span>
                        button or pasted and searched the url, you will be redirected to the <span class="fst-italic">About</span>
                        page.
                    </p>
                    <hr />

                </article>

                <article class="blog-post">
                    <h2 class="blog-post-title pb-4 mb-4 fst-italic" id="maps">
