                      By:
                      <a href="#"><%= user.firstName %> <%= user.lastName %> </a>
                    </p>
                    <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                      How to use the all restaurants cluster map
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        To use the map to view all restaurants, you can zoom in and out on the map to show different areas and clusters. You can also click on the <span class="fst-italic">unclustered map points</span> to be taken to a restaurant.
                    </p>
                    <hr />
                    <h3 class="blog-post-title">
                      How to use the single restaurant map
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        To use the map to view a single restaurant, you can zoom in and out on the map
                        to get a better view of the restaurant and quickly get to the restaurant.
                    </p>
                    <hr />
                    <button class="btn btn-light btn-lg"><a href="#top"> Back to Top <i class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-up"></i></a></button>

